<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENBP70A1306006" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Accelerator Pedal Assembly (Incorporating APP Sensor) Removal and Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A1306005">APP Sensor On-Vehicle Inspection</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<attention4>
<ptxt>
Failure to take proper precautions when handling the APP sensor assembly may lead to malfunction of the APP sensor.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not drop or otherwise expose the APP sensor assembly to large shock. Any APP sensor assembly that has received large shock must be replaced.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Keep the sensor section of the APP sensor assembly away from water.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention4>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
After replacing accelerator pedal assembly (incorporating APP sensor), calibrate throttle valve position. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A1306004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A1306006001" page = "2">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Disconnect negative (–) cable at battery.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Disconnect connector from accelerator pedal assembly (incorporating APP sensor).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Remove accelerator pedal assembly from its bracket.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A1306006002" page = "2">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A1306007">APP Sensor Inspection</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Reverse removal procedure noting the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten accelerator pedal assembly nuts (1) and accelerator pedal assembly bracket nuts (2) to specified torques.
</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T1C002">
<t-part>
Accelerator pedal assembly nut
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
5.5
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
0.56
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
4.0
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
<torqueitem id = "T1C003">
<t-part>
Accelerator pedal assembly bracket nut
</t-part>
<t-part1>
b
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
13
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
1.3
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
9.5
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
